About

This is a template blog. It is supposed to be used for the documentation of any kind of project. Posts with the category "Contributor" in the Front Matter will be shown in the section "Contributors". Posts with the category "Article" will be shown in the section "Articles".

This project is maintained by Jens Schnitzler. View on GitHub. Hosted on GitHub Pages. Works with Jekyll.
